overview: From 2025-10-30 to 2025-10-31, elizaos/elizaos.github.io had 0 new PRs (0 merged), 1 new issues, and 1 active contributors.

topIssues.title: Weekly Summary on profiles displaying incorrect week + date
topIssues.author: Vianvolaeus
topIssues.body: Looks like most Weekly Summaries on the leaderboard at stuck on week dated 13th-19th July 2025, though there are [some exceptions](https://elizaos.github.io/profile/madjin), where the date is different. Either way, appears to be incorrect range / date.

topContributors.summary: standujar: Focused on significant feature development and bug fixes, notably merging PR elizaos-plugins/plugin-solana#21 to enhance wallet functionality with lazyloading and HTTP routes, and addressing a critical bug in elizaos/eliza#6106 to ensure agent settings persistence. Their work primarily involved feature development, bug fixes, refactoring, and tests, with a focus on code and test files.

0xbbjoker: Focused on feature development, contributing a new static provider for listing available documents in elizaos-plugins/plugin-knowledge via PR #45, which involved modifying 6 files with a net addition of 246 lines. Their work today primarily involved feature and documentation tasks, touching both code and configuration files.
Vianvolaeus: Created one issue today, elizaos/elizaos.github.io#168, to report an incorrect display of week and date in weekly summaries on profiles.
